<img src="credit.gif" width="200" height="150" alt="" border="0" align="right">

<font class="title3">Credit card fraud reminder</font><br>
<br>
Don't automatically give out credit card information over the phone. If you doubt the legitimacy of a call to pay your City Light bill, you can reach us at <b>(206) 684-3000</b>. Utility account representatives can verify the status of your account.

